Robin Marshall, director of fixed 
income at Smith & Williamson Investment Management, discusses 
the outlook for Portuguese, Spanish and Italian sovereign bond 
yields, and the role of the  European Central Bank  in solving 
the euro-area debt crisis.   He speaks with Maryam Nemazee on Bloomberg Television’s 
“The Pulse.” (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 04:14
 